{"type":"message","id":"6c185ec7","parentId":"6e147504","timestamp":"2026-03-22T18:58:36.574Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sun 2026-03-22 19:58 GMT+1] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: Implementiere alle fehlenden Major Features für Mission Control v2:\n\n1. **Calendar** (`app/calendar/page.tsx`, `components/calendar/CalendarView.tsx`)\n   - FullCalendar Integration mit @fullcalendar/react\n   - Monats/Wochen/Tages-Ansicht\n   - Tasks als Events anzeigen\n   - Drag-and-Drop Terminierung\n\n2. **Projects UI** (`app/projects/page.tsx`, `components/projects/ProjectList.tsx`, `components/projects/ProjectDetail.tsx`)\n   - Projekt-Liste mit Fortschrittsbalken\n   - Projekt-Detail-Ansicht\n   - Charts mit Recharts für Task-Statistiken\n   - Verknüpfung zu Tasks\n\n3. **Analytics Dashboard** (`app/dashboard/page.tsx`, `components/analytics/StatsCards.tsx`)\n   - Task Completion Rate\n   - Agent Performance\n   - Projekt Health Score\n   - Recharts für Visualisierungen\n\n4. **Documents UI** (`app/docs/page.tsx`, `components/docs/DocList.tsx`, `components/docs/DocEditor.tsx`)\n   - Dokumenten-Liste\n   - Markdown Editor mit react-markdown\n   - Volltext-Suche (einfache Version)\n\n5. **Team/Agents UI** (`app/team/page.tsx`, `components/team/AgentList.tsx`)\n   - Agent-Übersicht\n   - Performance-Metriken\n   - Aktueller Task pro Agent\n\nNutze die bestehenden API-Routes:\n- /api/projects\n- /api/docs\n- /api/agents\n- /api/tasks\n\nStyle: Linear Dark Theme (bg-[#0a0a0a], purple accents)\n\nArbeite im Ordner: C:\\Users\\andre\\.openclaw\\workspace\\skills\\mission-control-v2"}],"timestamp":1774205916570}}
