{"type":"message","id":"8076cd9b","parentId":"fde67608","timestamp":"2026-03-22T18:59:49.378Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool_PQC2D8iXEEULea0uFyw38D3I","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"use client\"\n\nimport { ReactNode } from \"react\"\nimport { Sidebar } from \"./sidebar\"\nimport { Header } from \"./header\"\n\ninterface MainLayoutProps {\n  children: ReactNode\n}\n\nexport function MainLayout({ children }: MainLayoutProps) {\n  return (\n    <div className=\"min-h-screen bg-[#0a0a0a]\">\n      <Header />\n      <div className=\"flex\">\n        <Sidebar />\n        <main className=\"flex-1 ml-[240px] mt-14\">\n          <div className=\"p-8 max-w-[1400px] mx-auto\">\n            {children}\n          </div>\n        </main>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  )\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774205989373}}
{"type":"message","id":"80d27638","parentId":"8076cd9b","timestamp":"2026-03-22T18:59:57.728Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a good understanding of the project structure. Let me install the necessary dependencies first (FullCalendar and Recharts), then create all the required components and pages.\n\nLet me start implementing:\n\n1. First, install dependencies\n2. Create the Calendar components and page\n3. Create the Projects UI components and page\n4. Create the Analytics Dashboard with StatsCards\n5. Create the Documents UI components and page\n6. Create the Team/Agents UI components and page\n7. Update the sidebar to include new navigation items\n\nLet's start!","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Now I have a complete understanding of the project. Let me start implementing all the missing features. First, I'll install the required dependencies:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_WRZjIKwGWIgMC6TPzLsxsVa8","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd \"C:\\Users\\andre\\.openclaw\\workspace\\skills\\mission-control-v2\" ; npm install @fullcalendar/react @fullcalendar/core @fullcalendar/daygrid @fullcalendar/timegrid @fullcalendar/interaction recharts react-markdown remark-gfm","timeout":120000}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"kimi-k2-thinking","usage":{"input":284,"output":213,"cacheRead":79360,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":79857,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774205989384}}
